reviewText: Great firearms reviewed and used at a range.  Learn a lot and enjoy!  You'll see them up close an d learn about their history and use in the past.
an excellent job done by Larry again, i hope that he does more like this and covers as many weapons as possible, giving the viewer a well informed look at what is out there.
Season 2 has a different sort of approach to looking at the design details of the firearms. Packed full of knowledge and shooting demonstrations.
